Hello, this is my first tutorial about RSPS. I actually going to show you how to make your own Error System. I saw the Runescape's error system and I got a bit disapointed. I must mention that this isn't perfect. It's a simple base that you can work out your own way. Tons of things can be improved. 

Here is how it might look:
